</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">21.7 fmol</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">amount of Cl<sup>&#x02212;</sup> in ICS</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
