</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">89.8 fmol</td><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">amount of Cl<sup>&#x02212;</sup> in ECS</td></tr><tr><td align="left" rowspan="1" colspan="1">
